snippet.title: LAURE X EKDEV LIMBU - TIHAR SONG [OFFICIAL VIDEO 2025] | KABITA NEPALI
snippet.description:
Actually, I created this song long time ago but whenever I listen to it, I felt something incomplete and I thought that I could do lot of experiments to make this song more close towards the perfection. This year, finally, with the help, courage and push from my beloved people I am able to present you guys this beautiful masterpiece. 

‚ÄúTIHAR SONG‚Äù is an occasional song but if you dissect this creation musically and visually, you can find lots of interesting things, which will make your normal days; lightened and brighten up like Tihar. Happy Tihar to you all. May goddess Laxmi bless you and your family with wealth and good health. Jay Nepal üá≥üáµ

snippet.description:

CAST:
Prabhas as Sivudu & Baahubali, Rana Daggubati as Bhallaladeva, Anushka Shetty as Devasena, Tamannaah as Avanthika with Ramya Krishna, Nasser, Sathyaraj, Kiccha Sudeepa, Adivi Sesh, Rakesh Varre, Meka Ramakrishna.

CREW:

Goddess Lakshmi Mata is the goddess of wealth, wisdom, prosperity, grace, generosity and charm. A person who recites this Aarti with true devotion is blessed with wealth and prosperity and a good family life. The worship of Laxmi and the regular chanting of the chalisa is recommended, to those wishing to free their Karma of all the past misdeeds.

The biggest, spiciest ad film of the year is HERE! 
Atlee x Ranveer Singh team up with Sreeleela & Bobby Deol for the wildest cinematic explosion of action, drama, comedy & masala.

Watch the explosive trailer of AGENT CHING ATTACKS with jaw-dropping action, whistle-worthy drama, foot-tapping music, and masala so hot‚Ä¶ it‚Äôll set your screen on fire.

The full film premieres Sunday, October 19 exclusively on this channel.

WHAT TO EXPECT:
‚Ä¢ Ranveer Singh in his most powerful avatar yet as Agent Ching
‚Ä¢ Sreeleela adding spice and swagger as Agent Mirchi
‚Ä¢ Bobby Deol unleashing chaos as Professor White Noise
‚Ä¢ Signature Atlee scale, style & spectacle with a global A-list crew
‚Ä¢ A brand-new version of the iconic anthem ‚ÄúMy Name is Ranveer Ching‚Äù

From Bhatinda to Beijing, there‚Äôs only one king‚Ä¶ Ranveer Ching!

This is the BIGGEST celebration of Desi Chinese ever ‚Äî bold, flavourful, cinematic, and guaranteed to #AagLagaDe.

About Ching‚Äôs Secret - They say that to win Hindustani hearts even Chinese food became desi! And there‚Äôs only one Desi Chinese food brand that can make desi hearts beat faster ‚Äì Ching‚Äôs. Saucy. Spicy. Sweet and sour. Hot and sour. Crunchy. Slurpy. Zesty. Schezwani. Manchurian‚Ä¶ Whatever be the kind of Desi Chinese your palate craves for, only Ching‚Äôs can hit the spot with a perfect zing.

I ‚ô• Desi Chinese!

snippet.title: Rs 50000 Minecraft DeathSwap Challenge with a YouTuber!
snippet.description:
Rs 50000 Minecraft DeathSwap Challenge with a YouTuber!


Instagram pe 50k kar do: https://www.instagram.com/psd_1/

In this video, I do a Minecraft deathswap challenge with my YouTuber friend @MrLapis

snippet.title: Ujan Shakya - Baby (Official Music Video)
snippet.description:
MEY STUDIO & VISIONS MEDIA PRODUCTION
PRESENTS

BABY by Ujan Shakya || New Newari Song || New Nepal Bhasa Song || New Nepali Song

"Baby" explores the theme of love. It depicts the concept of love at first sight through a narrative that combines imagination and emotion. The piece is characterized as an emotional afrobeat , featuring a blend of Newari instruments.


Written, Music Produced & Performed by : UJAN SHAKYA

snippet.title: Dhurandhar - Title Track | Ranveer Singh, Shashwat Sachdev, Hanumankind, Jasmine Sandlas,Aditya Dhar
snippet.description:
It‚Äôs here. It‚Äôs fierce.
The wait is over ‚Äî the Dhurandhar Title Track (Jogi) is finally here!
Packed with fierce beats, bold voices, and unstoppable energy ‚Äî this one‚Äôs pure fire. üî•

Releasing on 5th December 2025

Credits: 
Jio Studios Presents
A B62 Studios Production

An Aditya Dhar Film
DHURANDHAR

Written, Directed and Produced by: Aditya Dhar
Produced by: Jyoti Deshpande
Produced by: Lokesh Dhar

Cast: Ranveer Singh | Sanjay Dutt | Akshaye Khanna | R. Madhavan | Arjun Rampal | Sara Arjun

Audio Credits:
Original Song Name: Na De Dil Pardesi Nu (Jogi)
Song name: Dhurandhar - Title Track 
Music: Shashwat Sachdev, Charanjit Ahuja
Produced and Arranged: Shashwat Sachdev
Singers: Hanumankind, Jasmine Sandlas, Sudhir Yaduvanshi, Shashwat Sachdev, Mohd. Sadiq, Ranjit Kaur
Lyrics: Hanumankind, Jasmine Sandlas, Babu Singh Maan
Music Video: Jayesh Shikarkhane & Team
Mix and mastered by Shadab Rayeen @ New Edge 
Assistant engineers: Jazbaat, Sohamm, Suryansh
HanumanKind vocals mixed by Akash Shravan

Lyrics:

Ladies and Gentlemen 
You are not ready for this 

Na de dil pardesi nu tainu nit da roona pai jau ga 
Na de dil pardesi nu tainu nit da roona pai jau ga
Nal ranje jogi de tainu jogan hauna pai jau ga

Mai ishq de allein zakhma de khud has has ke muh seen lan gi
Je jar mera mainu zehar zehar zehar

Each player starts by choosing an avatar and giving it an identity. They can then explore ROBLOX ‚Äî interacting with others by chatting, playing games, or collaborating on creative projects. Each player is also given their own piece of undeveloped real estate along with a virtual toolbox with which to design and build anything ‚Äî be it a navigable skyscraper, a working helicopter, a giant pinball machine, a multiplayer ‚ÄúCapture the Flag‚Äù game or some other, yet-to-be-dreamed-up creation. There is no cost for this first plot of virtual land. By participating and by building cool stuff, ROBLOX members can earn specialty badges as well as ROBLOX dollars (‚ÄúRobux‚Äù). In turn, they can shop the online catalog to purchase avatar clothing and accessories as well as premium building materials, interactive components, and working mechanisms.

Goddess Lakshmi Mata is the goddess of wealth, wisdom, prosperity, grace, generosity and charm.
